function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)
	
	Hydra.BossEncounterManuallyComplete(BOSS_ENCOUNTER_LEVEL_AREA);
	
	Hydra.Wait(0.25);
	
	tMonstersAll = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("Camp_FalconsRidge_Monsters");
	for i, actorID in ipairs(tMonstersAll) do
		if Hydra.ActorIsValid(actorID) then
			Hydra.ActorKill(actorID);
		end
	end
	
	--Hydra.WeatherOverride(Hydra.ActorGetWorld(idActorKiller), "weather_Kehjistan_physical")
	Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(CONV_PreClaim, idActorKiller)
	
	local tAllPlayers = Hydra.QuestGetParticipants()
     
    for i, idPlayer in ipairs(tAllPlayers) do
        -- Drop the TreasureClass, which contains both "always" and "first time" rewards
        -- The First Time stuff is conditioned by the flag that is set after the drop occurs
        Hydra.TreasureClassDropAtActorForPlayer(idActorKilled, "FirstTimeReward_Stronghold_OmathsRedoubt", idPlayer)
         
        -- Set the variable, to mark that this player has recieved a reward
        Hydra.SetPlayerVariableFlag(idPlayer, "FirstTimeReward_Stronghold_OmathsRedoubt")
    end
	
	Hydra.MusicOverride("Sanctuary_Eastern_Continent", "Music_Kehjistan_Omath_Victory")
end

local function UpdateSpawnTier()
	if nSpawnTier < nSpawnTierMax then 
		nSpawnTier = nSpawnTier+1 
	end
end

local function GetNewLane()

	local nRandIndex = Hydra.GetRandomInt(1, #tLaneKeyTemp);
	local sReturn = tLaneKeyTemp[nRandIndex];
	table.remove(tLaneKeyTemp, nRandIndex);
	
	if #tLaneKeyTemp <= 0 then 
		for i=1, #tSpawnLaneKeyValues do
			table.insert(tLaneKeyTemp, tSpawnLaneKeyValues[i]);
		end
	end
	
	return sReturn;
end

local function SpawnWave(nWaveCount)

	local idTeleport
	local sLaneKey = GetNewLane()

	for i2=1, #tSpawnTypeKeyValues do
		if Hydra.ActorIsValid(tSpawners[sLaneKey][tSpawnTypeKeyValues[i2]]) then
			--Teleport to area
			if i2==1 then 
				local idTeleport = tSpawners[sLaneKey][tSpawnTypeKeyValues[i2]] 
				Hydra.ActorTriggerPowerAtTargetsFeet(idBanshee, idTeleport, S_PWR_TELEPORT);
				Hydra.ActorSetAIState(idBanshee, "WaveSpawn");
				-- User Event for Callout
				Hydra.EventSend("CAMP_FALCONSRIDGE_WAVESPAWN", idBanshee);
			end	
			--Get spawn counts from wave composition table and spawn the wave	
			local nSpawnCount = Hydra.GetRandomInt(tSpawnTierCombos[nSpawnTier][tSpawnTypeKeyValues[i2]][1],tSpawnTierCombos[nSpawnTier][tSpawnTypeKeyValues[i2]][2])
			if nSpawnCount > 0 then
				for i3=1, nSpawnCount do
					Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdate(tSpawners[sLaneKey][tSpawnTypeKeyValues[i2]])
				end
				Hydra.Wait(Hydra.GetRandomFloat());
			end
		end
		--Enable trickle spawners in that area
		if Hydra.ActorIsValid(tTrickleSpawners[sLaneKey][i2]) then
			Hydra.ActorEnable(tTrickleSpawners[sLaneKey][i2]);
		end
		--Enable phalanx in that area
		if Hydra.ActorIsValid(tPhalanx[sLaneKey][i2]) then
			Hydra.ActorEnable(tPhalanx[sLaneKey][i2]);
		end
	end 
	
--	Hydra.TraceScreen(sLaneKey,"wave spawned")	
	UpdateSpawnTier();
		
end
